Here’s a simple `index.html` you can drop into the repo to act as a clean landing page linking to each issue: [github](https://github.com/Longball-debug/Longfball-Newsletter)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Longball Gazette – Newsletter Hub</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1020;
      --card-bg: #151b30;
      --accent: #f5b301;
      --accent-soft: #f5b30122;
      --text: #f5f7ff;
      --muted: #a4acc4;
      --link: #61dafb;
      --link-hover: #9be3ff;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1f2942 0, #050713 55%, #020308 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .shell {
      max-width: 880px;
      width: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #151b30ee, #050713ee);
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #262f4a;
      box-shadow:
        0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
        0 0 0 1px #050713;
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem 2.4rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .shell::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -40%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0% 0%, rgba(245, 179, 1, 0.14), transparent 58%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(97, 218, 251, 0.14), transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .tag-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 0.18rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #30374f;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, #1e2742, #090c18);
      margin-left: 0.75rem;
    }

    header h1 span.logo-dot {
      width: 0.55rem;
      height: 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fff, var(--accent));
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(245, 179, 1, 0.8);
    }

    header p {
      margin-top: 0.55rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 540px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .meta-row {
      margin-top: 1.1rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem 1.4rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .meta-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background-color: rgba(4, 7, 18, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid #262f4a;
    }

    .meta-pill span.dot {
      width: 0.35rem;
      height: 0.35rem;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #25d366;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.8);
    }

    .grid {
      margin-top: 1.9rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, #202846, #090d1a 60%);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1rem 1rem 0.95rem;
      border: 1px solid #262f4a;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition:
        transform 160ms ease-out,
        box-shadow 160ms ease-out,
        border-color 160ms ease-out,
        background-position 160ms ease-out;
      background-size: 220% 220%;
      background-position: 0% 0%;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow:
        0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(245, 179, 1, 0.25);
      background-position: 25% 25%;
    }

    .card-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .card-label {
      font-size: 0.64rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .card-sub {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .card-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 0.1rem;
    }

    .card-meta span.date {
      color: #c4c9e6;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .card-meta span.read-time {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
    }

    .card-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--link);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .card-link svg {
      width: 0.85rem;
      height: 0.85rem;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .card:hover .card-link {
      color: var(--link-hover);
    }

    .card:hover .card-link svg path {
      stroke: var(--link-hover);
    }

    .card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 0, rgba(245, 179, 1, 0.06), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 160ms ease-out;
    }

    .card:hover::after {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .card-tag-row {
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
    }

    .card-tag {
      padding: 0.12rem 0.45rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245, 179, 1, 0.4);
      background-color: var(--accent-soft);
      color: #fbe9b0;
    }

    .card-tag.secondary {
      border-color: #303a58;
      background-color: rgba(55, 65, 110, 0.7);
      color: #d5defa;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--link);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: var(--link-hover);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .shell {
        padding: 1.5rem 1.3rem 1.8rem;
      }
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      header h1 {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
      }
      header p {
        font-size: 0.88rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <header>
      <h1>
        <span class="logo-dot"></span>
        Longball Gazette
        <span class="tag-pill">League Newsletter</span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to the Longball newsletter hub. Pick an issue below to dive into preseason notes, Opening Day storylines,
        and the week-by-week grind of the 2026 campaign.
      </p>
      <div class="meta-row">
        <div class="meta-pill">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span>Updated weekly in-season</span>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-pill">
          <span>Season</span> · <strong>2026</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="grid" aria-label="Newsletter issues">
      <!-- Preseason -->
      <article class="card" onclick="location.href='longball2026_preseason.html'">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="card-title">2026 Preseason Preview</h2>
          <span class="card-label">Issue 0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="card-sub">
          Power rankings, draft fallout, and a first look at who’s chasing the pennant before a single pitch is thrown.
        </p>
        <div class="card-tag-row">
          <span class="card-tag">Preseason</span>
          <span class="card-tag secondary">Power rankings</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span class="date">March 2026</span>
          <span class="read-time">~7 min read</span>
        </div>
        <a class="card-link" href="longball2026_preseason.html">
          Read issue
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 8h7M8 4l3 4-3 4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Opening Day -->
      <article class="card" onclick="location.href='longball_gazette_opening_day.html'">
        <div class="card-header">
