        </p>
        <div class="card-tag-row">
          <span class="card-tag">Opening Day</span>
          <span class="card-tag secondary">Storylines</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span class="date">Opening Day 2026</span>
          <span class="read-time">~6 min read</span>
        </div>
        <a class="card-link" href="longball_gazette_opening_day.html">
          Read issue
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 8h7M8 4l3 4-3 4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Week 1 -->
      <article class="card" onclick="location.href='longball_gazette_week1.html'">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="card-title">Week 1 Gazette</h2>
          <span class="card-label">Issue 2</span>
        </div>
        <p class="card-sub">
          First-week overreactions, breakout alarms, and early standings that are definitely not getting screenshotted.
        </p>
        <div class="card-tag-row">
          <span class="card-tag">Week 1</span>
          <span class="card-tag secondary">Recap</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span class="date">Week 1 · 2026</span>
          <span class="read-time">~6 min read</span>
        </div>
        <a class="card-link" href="longball_gazette_week1.html">
          Read issue
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 8h7M8 4l3 4-3 4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Placeholder / future issues -->
      <article class="card" onclick="window.open('https://github.com/Longball-debug/Longfball-Newsletter', '_blank')">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="card-title">Archive & Latest Deploy</h2>
          <span class="card-label">GitHub</span>
        </div>
        <p class="card-sub">
          Browse every past issue, check deployment history, or grab the raw HTML straight from the Longball Gazette repo.
        </p>
        <div class="card-tag-row">
          <span class="card-tag secondary">Full archive</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span class="date">Live via GitHub Pages</span>
          <span class="read-time">Repo view</span>
        </div>
        <a class="card-link" href="https://github.com/Longball-debug/Longfball-Newsletter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          View on GitHub
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M6 4h6v6M4 12l8-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
